 na ljubav

715
00:33:19,500 --> 00:33:20,200
 uzrća

716
00:33:20,200 --> 00:33:22,200
 kako?

717
00:33:22,200 --> 00:33:24,060
 Bravo.

718
00:33:24,060 --> 00:33:26,240
 To što me pitaš,

719
00:33:26,240 --> 00:33:26,900
 pa normalno,

720
00:33:26,900 --> 00:33:27,440
 je li tako?

721
00:33:27,440 --> 00:33:28,840
 Vidiš.

722
00:33:28,840 --> 00:33:31,300
 Kako je jednostavno,

723
00:33:31,300 --> 00:33:31,600
 je li da?

724
00:33:31,600 --> 00:33:33,740
 Nema mistike.

725
00:33:33,740 --> 00:33:35,480
 Logika.

726
00:33:35,480 --> 00:33:37,200
 Pa muškima treba logika.

727
00:33:37,200 --> 00:33:42,480
 Dakle,

728
00:33:42,480 --> 00:33:43,580
 mi kažemo

729
00:33:43,580 --> 00:33:44,580
 zapovjed ljubavi,

730
00:33:44,580 --> 00:33:46,340
 ali to je toliko logično.

731
00:33:46,340 --> 00:33:48,300
 Ljubi Boga svoga,

732
00:33:48,300 --> 00:33:49,040
 mogu ga ljubiti

733
00:33:49,040 --> 00:33:49,420
 jedino

734
00:33:49,420 --> 00:33:50,540
 ako sam ljubljena.

735
00:33:50,540 --> 00:33:52,300
 To vi sad,

736
00:33:52,300 --> 00:33:52,880
 dečki cure,

737
00:33:52,880 --> 00:33:53,340
 znate,

738
00:33:53,340 --> 00:33:54,680
 možete i za nekim patiti,

739
00:33:54,680 --> 00:33:55,080
 ali ako

740
00:33:55,080 --> 00:33:56,280
 on tebe

741
00:33:56,280 --> 00:33:58,040
 ne događa se.

742
00:33:58,040 --> 00:33:59,520
 Prema tome,

743
00:33:59,520 --> 00:34:00,580
 uvijek je Bog prvi,

744
00:34:00,580 --> 00:34:01,480
 zapamti se to.

745
00:34:01,480 --> 00:34:03,540
 I ti uzrećaš.

746
00:34:03,540 --> 00:34:05,840
 I sada kaže,

747
00:34:05,840 --> 00:34:06,160
 znači,

748
00:34:06,160 --> 00:34:07,000
 svim srcem svojim,

749
00:34:07,000 --> 00:34:07,240
 znači,

750
00:34:07,240 --> 00:34:07,800
 cijelo,

751
00:34:07,800 --> 00:34:08,060
 ono,

752
00:34:08,060 --> 00:34:09,000
 kako se ti razvioš

753
00:34:09,000 --> 00:34:09,420
 kao osoba,

754
00:34:09,420 --> 00:34:10,280
 tako ta ljubav

755
00:34:10,280 --> 00:34:10,660
 dobiva

756
00:34:10,660 --> 00:34:11,980
 druge dimenzije.

757
00:34:11,980 --> 00:34:14,140
 i nastavak toga je,

758
00:34:14,140 --> 00:34:16,000
 a bližnjega svoga

759
00:34:16,000 --> 00:34:18,860
 kao samoga sebe.

760
00:34:18,860 --> 00:34:19,400
 E sad,

761
00:34:19,400 --> 00:34:19,780
 dolazimo,

762
00:34:19,780 --> 00:34:21,140
 ne znam kako ste vi odgajani,

763
00:34:21,140 --> 00:34:23,000
 ali sam ja odgajana.

764
00:34:23,000 --> 00:34:24,960
 Ne smije smisliti na sebe.

765
00:34:24,960 --> 00:34:26,480
 To je sebičnost.

766
00:34:27,380 --> 00:34:28,500
 Jeste vi tako odgajani?

767
00:34:28,500 --> 00:34:30,280
 Rečina,

768
00:34:30,280 --> 00:34:30,940
 posebno ovo,

769
00:34:30,940 --> 00:34:31,440
 B i H.

770
00:34:31,440 --> 00:34:35,540
 Ne smiješ na sebe misliti.

771
00:34:35,540 --> 00:34:36,160
 Kako no?

772
00:34:36,160 --> 00:34:39,440
 Koje su one naše tri rečenice

773
00:34:39,440 --> 00:34:40,560
 odgojne?

774
00:34:40,560 --> 00:34:42,900
 Šuti i trpi.

775
00:34:42,900 --> 00:34:44,480
 Jel da?

776
00:34:44,480 --> 00:34:48,160
 Neki je njima dobro,

777
00:34:48,160 --> 00:34:49,080
 meni kako bude.

778
00:34:49,080 --> 00:34:52,820
 I prešuti ću,

779
00:34:52,820 --> 00:34:53,540
 izdržat ću,

780
00:34:53,540 --> 00:34:54,520
 Radmira u kući.

781
00:34:56,660 --> 00:34:58,060
 i tebe nema.

782
00:34:58,060 --> 00:35:02,480
 Izgubiš se.

783
00:35:02,480 --> 00:35:03,440
 Nemate.

784
00:35:03,440 --> 00:35:05,080
 Ti si ono od tepih

785
00:35:05,080 --> 00:35:06,060
 po kome svi drugi

786
00:35:06,060 --> 00:35:07,320
 mogu slobodno hodati.

787
00:35:07,320 --> 00:35:07,700
 Reči,

788
00:35:07,700 --> 00:35:08,600
 čist je,

789
00:35:08,600 --> 00:35:09,320
 nije čisto.

790
00:35:09,320 --> 00:35:11,100
 Moglo je ovo zategnuto biti,

791
00:35:11,100 --> 00:35:11,720
 moglo je ovako,

792
00:35:11,720 --> 00:35:12,380
 moglo je onako.

793
00:35:12,380 --> 00:35:14,860
 Izgubiš taj osjećaj dostojanstva,

794
00:35:14,860 --> 00:35:15,560
 vrednovanje,

795
00:35:15,560 --> 00:35:16,320
 tako dalje.

796
00:35:16,320 --> 00:35:17,320
 Dakle,

797
00:35:17,320 --> 00:35:18,840
 ljubiti bližnjega svoga

798
00:35:18,840 --> 00:35:19,880
 kao samog sebe.

799
00:35:19,880 --> 00:35:21,700
 Što bi to značilo?

800
00:35:21,700 --> 00:35:22,380
 Upravo ovo.

801
00:35:22,380 --> 00:35:22,960
 Znači,

802
00:35:22,960 --> 00:35:24,840
 izliječiti ove sve ranjenosti,

803
00:35:24,840 --> 00:35:26,000
 obnoviti,

804
00:35:26,000 --> 00:35:28,100
 ozdraviti svoje dostojanstva.

805
00:35:28,100 --> 00:35:31,440
 Jer dostojanstvo nije nešto

806
00:35:31,440 --> 00:35:32,560
 što ti je dao čovjek.

807
00:35:32,560 --> 00:35:33,620
 Niti mama,

808
00:35:33,620 --> 00:35:34,660
 niti tata,

809
00:35:34,660 --> 00:35:35,760
 niti fakultet,

810
00:35:35,760 --> 00:35:36,560
 niti šef,

811
00:35:36,560 --> 00:35:37,600
 niti dijete,

812
00:35:37,600 --> 00:35:38,540
 niti muž,

813
00:35:38,540 --> 00:35:39,240
 niti žena,

814
00:35:39,240 --> 00:35:41,140
 niti to što si hrvat katolik.

815
00:35:41,140 --> 00:35:41,720
 Ne.

816
00:35:43,720 --> 00:35:44,900
 dostojanstvo ti daje

817
00:35:44,900 --> 00:35:46,080
 bog,

818
00:35:46,080 --> 00:35:47,460
 oteca.

819
00:35:47,460 --> 00:35:53,180
 Kad to final negdje sjedne u tebi,

820
00:35:53,180 --> 00:35:54,180
 aha,

821
00:35:54,180 --> 00:35:55,680
 znači,

822
00:35:55,680 --> 00:35:56,780
 ja sam iljubljena,

823
00:35:56,780 --> 00:35:59,700
 ja imam izvor svoga dostojanstva,

824
00:35:59,700 --> 00:36:01,500
 e, nećeš pajdoviše,

825
00:36:01,500 --> 00:36:03,000
 nećeš.

826
00:36:05,660 --> 00:36:08,020
 ti ozdravljaš u svojoj srčiki,

827
00:36:08,020 --> 00:36:10,420
 u svoje cjelovitosti.

828
00:36:10,420 --> 00:36:11,820
 Ozdravljaš.

829
00:36:11,820 --> 00:36:12,640
 Zašto?

830
00:36:12,640 --> 00:36:15,720
 Zato što odjednom imaš drugi pogled na samog sebe.

831
00:36:15,720 --> 00:36:16,720
 Na sebe.

832
00:36:16,720 --> 00:36:18,120
 Mijenjati se.

833
00:36:18,120 --> 00:36:23,920
 Dobivaš ti u svojim vlastitim očima jednu drugu vrijednost.

834
00:36:24,960 --> 00:36:26,860
 I odjednom svi smo im prošli to

835
00:36:26,860 --> 00:36:29,860
 da ti drugi ljudi tebe određuju

836
00:36:29,860 --> 00:36:31,300
 kako ti treba živjeti,

837
00:36:31,300 --> 00:36:32,540
 šta ti trebaš rati,

838
00:36:32,540 --> 00:36:33,400
 trebaš li ovo,

839
00:36:33,400 --> 00:36:34,220
 trebaš li ono.

840
00:36:34,220 --> 00:36:37,220
 I odjednom ti počebaš slušati onoga

841
00:36:37,220 --> 00:36:39,520
 koji te satka u krilu majčinu

842
00:36:39,520 --> 00:36:40,420
 i kaže,

843
00:36:40,420 --> 00:36:41,900
 pa valjda ja znam

844
00:36:41,900 --> 00:36:44,380
 šta sam ja stavio u tebe.

845
00:36:44,380 --> 00:36:47,460
 Valjda je to moja ingerencija,

846
00:36:47,460 --> 00:36:49,040
 a nije stvorenja.

847
00:36:49,040 --> 00:36:51,120
 Pa bila to i mama,

848
00:36:51,120 --> 00:36:51,900
 i tata,

849
00:36:51,900 --> 00:36:52,600
 i muž,

850
00:36:52,600 --> 00:36:53,940
 i svećenik,

851
00:36:53,940 --> 00:36:54,780
 i duhovnik,

852
00:36:54,780 --> 00:36:55,600
 i zajednica,

853
00:36:55,600 --> 00:36:56,920
 i kogod.

854
00:36:56,920 --> 00:36:59,560
 Žena, naravno.

855
00:36:59,560 --> 00:37:01,680
 To.

856
00:37:01,680 --> 00:37:05,160
 Razumijete?

857
00:37:05,160 --> 00:37:08,440
 Dakle, u tom smislu negdje,

858
00:37:08,440 --> 00:37:10,580
 znači, ljubiti sebe,

859
00:37:10,580 --> 00:37:11,720
 kad sam ja to shvatila,

860
00:37:11,720 --> 00:37:14,200
 kad sam se digla izna tih plitkih

861
00:37:14,200 --> 00:37:16,040
 ljudskih načina razmišljanja,

862
00:37:16,040 --> 00:37:18,100
 ljubiti sebe, znači,

863
00:37:18,100 --> 00:37:22,600
 uzljubiti Božju sliku o meni u meni.

864
00:37:25,600 --> 00:37:26,180
 Vidite?

865
00:37:26,180 --> 00:37:26,300
 Vidite?

866
00:37:26,300 --> 00:37:29,060
 Kako me je on,

867
00:37:29,060 --> 00:37:30,280
 to je poljubac,

868
00:37:30,280 --> 00:37:32,440
 Bog je poljubio svakog od nas.

869
00:37:32,440 --> 00:37:35,360
 U dušu, mi imamo taj poljubac Boži u sebi.

870
00:37:35,360 --> 00:37:36,420
 E to,

871
00:37:36,420 --> 00:37:38,140
 to čuvaj,

872
00:37:38,140 --> 00:37:39,160
 to čisti,

873
00:37:39,160 --> 00:37:41,060
 to su ovi slojevi šta su

874
00:37:41,060 --> 00:37:43,300
 međuljudski odnosi i situacije

875
00:37:43,300 --> 00:37:44,820
 naslagalo,

876
00:37:44,820 --> 00:37:47,000
 podošli iznad tebe.

877
00:37:48,800 --> 00:37:49,760
 otvoriti to,

878
00:37:49,760 --> 00:37:50,800
 to očistiti,

879
00:37:50,800 --> 00:37:51,500
 to skirati,

880
00:37:51,500 --> 00:37:53,320
 to su te naše ranjenosti,

881
00:37:53,320 --> 00:37:55,140
 to su te naše negativne sjećanja,

882
00:37:55,140 --> 00:37:57,720
 naše negativne misli.

883
00:37:57,720 --> 00:37:59,080
 To hrpa ljudi,

884
00:37:59,080 --> 00:38:00,180
 meni kako god dođe,

885
00:38:00,180 --> 00:38:02,540
 pa šta god započne,

886
00:38:02,540 --> 00:38:03,340
 znaš, Marija,

887
00:38:03,340 --> 00:38:03,660
 ali,

888
00:38:03,660 --> 00:38:04,200
 znaš,

889
00:38:04,200 --> 00:38:04,660
 kad to,

890
00:38:04,660 --> 00:38:05,260
 ako to,

891
00:38:05,260 --> 00:38:06,000
 pa ja govorim,

892
00:38:06,000 --> 00:38:06,340
 čekaj,

893
00:38:06,340 --> 00:38:07,240
 danas je srijeda.

894
00:38:07,240 --> 00:38:10,680
 Ti meni pičaš o nečemu što će desiti za deset dana,

895
00:38:10,680 --> 00:38:11,720
 ti si tu.

896
00:38:11,720 --> 00:38:13,940
 Još biš živa.

897
00:38:13,940 --> 00:38:19,080
 Samo sad stanite prazniste.

898
00:38:19,080 --> 00:38:21,080
 Ko to ne radi?

899
00:38:21,080 --> 00:38:23,500
 Šta ako?

900
00:38:23,500 --> 00:38:25,280
 Čuvena rečenica.

901
00:38:25,280 --> 00:38:27,000
 Da,

902
00:38:27,000 --> 00:38:27,980
 ali.

903
00:38:27,980 --> 00:38:33,360
 I sad mi kako ko ziđe dalje.

904
00:38:35,260 --> 00:38:38,000
 Kao pristajemo na Boži plan,

905
00:38:38,000 --> 00:38:39,580
 kažemo mi njemu da,

906
00:38:39,580 --> 00:38:41,040
 ali,

907
00:38:41,040 --> 00:38:42,820
 znaš ti Bož,

908
00:38:42,820 --> 00:38:44,660
 ne znaš ti kakva je ona,

909
00:38:44,660 --> 00:38:45,540
 kakav je on.

910
00:38:45,540 --> 00:38:52,680
 Vidite?

911
00:38:52,680 --> 00:38:58,100
 To je taj jedan totalni zaokret u nama,

912
00:38:58,100 --> 00:39:01,440
 kada počinamo sebe doživljavati

913
00:39:01,440 --> 00:39:04,120
 kao ljubljeno, vrednovano,

914
00:39:04,740 --> 00:39:06,020
 dragocjeno biće.

915
00:39:06,020 --> 00:39:11,060
 I da mi nismo ono

916
00:39:11,060 --> 00:39:13,380
 što drugi o nama misle,

917
00:39:13,380 --> 00:39:16,040
 što drugi o nama govore,

918
00:39:16,040 --> 00:39:18,380
 što drugi od nas očekuju.

919
00:39:18,380 --> 00:39:19,980
 Mjera tvoja,

920
00:39:19,980 --> 00:39:21,100
 mladi gospodine,

921
00:39:21,100 --> 00:39:23,200
 oženjeni, vidjela sam da imaš veru,

922
00:39:23,200 --> 00:39:25,780
 nije ono što tvoja žena

923
00:39:25,780 --> 00:39:26,940
 i tvoja djeca

924
00:39:26,940 --> 00:39:28,540
 misle ili šef

925
00:39:28,540 --> 00:39:29,400
 o tebi.

926
00:39:31,740 --> 00:39:33,080
 možda ima istine u nekim,

927
00:39:33,080 --> 00:39:35,460
 kako bi rekla,

928
00:39:35,460 --> 00:39:38,380
 procjenama, ocjenama doživljaje tebe.

929
00:39:38,380 --> 00:39:41,840
 Ali temeljna istina u svakom od nas je ono,

930
00:39:41,840 --> 00:39:44,400
 kako me Bog doživljava i gleda.

931
00:39:44,760 --> 00:39:46,820
 A on te uvijek gleda s ljubavljom.

932
00:39:46,820 --> 00:39:48,880
 On je uvijek za tebe.

933
00:39:48,880 --> 00:39:51,660
 I zato,

934
00:39:51,660 --> 00:39:53,060
 zato,

935
00:39:53,060 --> 00:39:55,180
 je strašno važno,

936
00:39:55,180 --> 00:39:58,160
 kada tebi to nekako se otvori,

937
00:39:58,160 --> 00:39:59,360
 a kada vidiš,

938
00:39:59,360 --> 00:40:00,520
 Bože moj,

939
00:40:00,520 --> 00:40:02,140
 koliko sam ja griješila,

940
00:40:02,140 --> 00:40:04,200
 koliko ja sam fulala,

941
00:40:04,200 --> 00:40:06,740
 koliko sam ja krivih izbora u životu,

942
00:40:06,740 --> 00:40:07,780
 napravo i tako dalje.

943
00:40:08,180 --> 00:40:08,540
 Dakle,

944
00:40:08,540 --> 00:40:11,720
 blagoslovljeno je to prosvjetljenje

945
00:40:11,720 --> 00:40:12,500
 kada vidiš

946
00:40:12,500 --> 00:40:15,920
 da si na neki način krivo usmjerio svoj život

947
00:40:15,920 --> 00:40:16,840
 u nekim izborima,

948
00:40:16,840 --> 00:40:18,580
 u nekim situacijama i tako dalje.

949
00:40:18,580 --> 00:40:20,160
 Ali ti sad znaš,

950
00:40:20,160 --> 00:40:22,000
 ali ti meni praštaš

951
00:40:22,000 --> 00:40:24,500
 i ja neću biti rob svoje prošlosti.

952
00:40:29,460 --> 00:40:30,900
 Baša zajednica se zove

953
00:40:30,900 --> 00:40:31,960
 na novo rođeni.

954
00:40:31,960 --> 00:40:33,480
 Je li tako?

955
00:40:33,480 --> 00:40:37,760
 Svaka osoba

956
00:40:37,760 --> 00:40:40,900
 koja je u istinu doživjela,

957
00:40:40,900 --> 00:40:43,180
 a moguće ne jednom,

958
00:40:43,180 --> 00:40:45,520
 ja sam to puno puta doživjela

959
00:40:45,520 --> 00:40:46,480
 u svom životu,

960
00:40:46,480 --> 00:40:48,860
 da me je Bog na novo rodio.

961
00:40:48,860 --> 00:40:51,560
 To nije jednom.

962
00:40:51,560 --> 00:40:54,900
 Ali to nisu osjećaj,

963
00:40:54,900 --> 00:40:56,800
 to nisu doživljaj,

964
00:40:56,800 --> 00:40:58,400
 to nisu malo.

965
00:40:59,460 --> 00:41:01,940
 To je dubinski nešto.

966
00:41:01,940 --> 00:41:03,440
 To je ono što kažu

967
00:41:03,440 --> 00:41:04,420
 resetirace.

968
00:41:04,420 --> 00:41:06,220
 Popularan je,

969
00:41:06,220 --> 00:41:07,640
 oprost, uvijek šušni.

970
00:41:07,640 --> 00:41:09,520
 Popularan je izraz,

971
00:41:09,520 --> 00:41:11,280
 ono, da te vrati

972
00:41:11,280 --> 00:41:12,620
 na tvorničke postavke.

973
00:41:12,620 --> 00:41:14,440
 To je sad zove mlade,

974
00:41:14,440 --> 00:41:17,480
 da se vratiš na tvorničke postavke.

975
00:41:17,480 --> 00:41:19,460
 To znači baš onako

976
00:41:19,460 --> 00:41:20,720
 poredati

977
00:41:20,720 --> 00:41:22,960
 te istine osobi

978
00:41:22,960 --> 00:41:24,440
 onako kako je Bog zamislio.

979
00:41:24,440 --> 00:41:27,200
 I to je tako moguće

980
00:41:27,200 --> 00:41:28,720
 i tako je jednostavno.

981
00:41:29,080 --> 00:41:31,260
 nije nikakva velika mantra,

982
00:41:31,260 --> 00:41:32,920
 nije nikakav veliki napor,

983
00:41:32,920 --> 00:41:34,240
