00:42:00,960 --> 00:42:02,800
 i ostvarene osobe.

1001
00:42:05,800 --> 00:42:07,800
 sretne i ostvarene osobe,

1002
00:42:07,800 --> 00:42:09,560
 ne individuji,

1003
00:42:09,560 --> 00:42:10,540
