00:44:19,500 --> 00:44:24,340
 Je li vam sjeda?

1068
00:44:24,340 --> 00:44:26,820
 Dobro, drago mi je.

1069
00:44:26,820 --> 00:44:29,620
 Zato je život lijep.

1070
00:44:29,620 --> 00:44:32,200
 Ja se sjećam,

1071
00:44:32,200 --> 00:44:36,100
