1105
00:45:35,220 --> 00:45:35,720
 meni je more,

1106
00:45:35,720 --> 00:45:36,560
 tak, tak,

1107
00:45:36,560 --> 00:45:37,460
 slano,

1108
00:45:37,460 --> 00:45:40,300
 ali rijeka vam je čudojena,

1109
00:45:40,300 --> 00:45:43,200
 uvijek nešto se događa,

1110
00:45:43,200 --> 00:45:44,540
 voda teče,

1111
00:45:44,540 --> 00:45:45,400
 uvijek ista voda,

1112
00:45:45,400 --> 00:45:46,240
 a nije ista,

1113
00:45:46,240 --> 00:45:48,100
 voda, voda,

1114
00:45:48,100 --> 00:45:49,120
 ali nije ista,

1115
00:45:49,120 --> 00:45:50,560
 pa ono valovi,

1116
00:45:50,560 --> 00:45:51,280
