00:46:56,380 --> 00:46:59,120
 razumijete,

1162
00:46:59,120 --> 00:47:02,020
 ja sam imala iskusta ljepote,

1163
00:47:02,020 --> 00:47:03,600
 o tome govorim,

1164
00:47:03,600 --> 00:47:05,880
 iskusta ljepote,

1165
00:47:08,700 --> 00:47:09,500
 i da kože,

1166
00:47:09,500 --> 00:47:11,060
