1173
00:47:18,240 --> 00:47:18,920
 pa vidimo ono,

1174
00:47:18,920 --> 00:47:20,900
 pa padali ceo neko zvijezde,

1175
00:47:20,900 --> 00:47:21,540
 i tako dalje,

1176
00:47:22,420 --> 00:47:23,580
 tebi je išao duh,

1177
00:47:23,580 --> 00:47:24,820
