1182
00:47:32,760 --> 00:47:34,380
 i sve stvara,

1183
00:47:34,380 --> 00:47:36,120
 i sve uzdržava,

1184
00:47:36,120 --> 00:47:37,120
 hej,

1185
00:47:37,120 --> 00:47:40,600
 sve uzdržava,

1186
00:47:40,600 --> 00:47:42,080
 znači,

1187
00:47:42,080 --> 00:47:45,080
 ima neko ko vodi brigu o sve u što je stvoreno,

1188
00:47:45,080 --> 00:47:48,240
